name: Hungry Kitty (frankiex3)
description:
# WIP

Best played in fullscreen.

Kitty is hungry!

Get fishies to satisfy kitty's hunger.  P.S. YOU CANNOT RESIST THIS FACE. 

What is this game?

A poorly executed adaptation of the snake game.  :') It was supposed to be less boxy....
More like this... 

I had GRAND PLANS to make the snake game aesthetic af, create a dog version and even make other mini games with animals but ah. Alas, procrastination was my biggest downfall.
